12 graduate degree nurse educator, from which the Governor shall make an
13 appointment as necessary by October 1, 2024. Thereafter, by March 1 of the
14 year in which the term of the graduate degree nurse educator expires, the
15 Kentucky League for Nursing shall submit to the Governor two (2) names of
16 qualified individuals for the appointment as a graduate degree nurse educator,
17 from which the Governor shall make an appointment as necessary by July 1.
18 (h)[ By March 1, 2025, and thereafter on March 1 of the year in which the term of
